{"tid":1642940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港競爭力攀上全球第三 僅次星美 未反映示威影響","createTime":"2019-10-10T02:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T02:35:26.000Z","uid":56881,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3efe2181b62e1d4a775e749b085d60430137dd4e","tid":1642940,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:17:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%8A%9B%E6%94%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89-%E5%83%85%E6%AC%A1%E6%98%9F%E7%BE%8E-%E6%9C%AA%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-195800832.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2594%2580%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589-%25E5%2583%2585%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25BE%258E-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2598%25A0%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF-195800832.html&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5wxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=d0de4124\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%8A%9B%E6%94%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89-%E5%83%85%E6%AC%A1%E6%98%9F%E7%BE%8E-%E6%9C%AA%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-195800832.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/z5dhjd97HHQDuJEcMj0w.w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/hkej.com/f42c0ffdecbba2a540a869b0c77834dc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fz5dhjd97HHQDuJEcMj0w.w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fhkej.com%2Ff42c0ffdecbba2a540a869b0c77834dc&h=fcf87cb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港競爭力攀上全球第三 僅次星美 未反映示威影響<br />\n<br />\n世界經濟論壇（WEF）發表2019年度《全球競爭力報告》，香港的競爭力躍升4位，排名居全球第三，僅次於新加坡和美國；新加坡今年則躍升一級，取代美國成為全球最具競爭力的經濟體。報告指出，香港弱點在於創新方面，相關排名只得26位。不過，調查在今年初進行，報告未反映本港6月起持續至今反修例示威的影響。<br />\n<br />\n創新能力及勞工權益遜色<br />\n<br />\n報告根據12項指標，評估141個經濟體的全球競爭力，香港取得83.1分。本港有4項指標排名第一，包括宏觀經濟穩定性、衞生、金融體系和產品市場；向來是本港強項的基礎設施，以及資訊與通訊科技應用則排第三。<br />\n<br />\n香港最弱一環仍舊是創新能力，在全球排名26，遠遠落後排13的新加坡12分；在勞工權益保障方面，香港也較新加坡遜色，工人權益得分在全球排名116位。另外，香港在未來勞動力技能表現亦較差，只排名第36位。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡今年力壓美國，以84.8分成為全球最具競爭力的經濟體，報告點評，新加坡是世界上最開放的經濟體，在12個分項指標中，有10項表現都名列前茅，當中在基礎設施排名第一，認為在港口和機場的服務效率，以及海上運輸連接也奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n至於美國得分83.7分，較去年跌1.9分，排名亦下滑1級至第二位。但美國仍然保持創新強國的地位，商業活力也稱霸，創新能力則位列第二。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好想知邊個無左香港唔得呢<br />\n示威加強競爭力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71445e03cfdd91b5046076515e4379f78c4b0419","tid":1642940,"uid":48080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:19:41.000Z","msg":"要不是有香港人示威 中國早就完蛋了"},{"pid":"fc8f175f7026ae843fafd629aec3c5e085b52767","tid":1642940,"uid":189157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"咁樣都獨立唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4152757d7638c1df6913440a662963628a976001","tid":1642940,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"深圳呢，上海呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec6262647a20a8634412ba3aa75182d5a9d6630","tid":1642940,"uid":77092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:21:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cae24ca5f2f74673c4c96e1879b46dabb42ce579","tid":1642940,"uid":55941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4152757d7638c1df6913440a662963628a976001","tid":1642940,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"深圳呢，上海呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:21:41.000Z","msg":"係榜尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"